column5: We are heading to Press Lake Camp on Fri. 6/29 and will be fishing Sat. 6/30 to Fri. 7/6. Looking to see if anyone has been there recently and can give us a report on how fishing was? It will be our first time at this resort and we are really looking forward to it. We have heard a lot of good things about the lake, resort, and the owners. Thanks!
